e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>天文台道秋田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫做平平地食到鐵板燒<br />\n但唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別個炒飯<br />\n我食諾士佛台分店 無下次</blockquote><br />\n海鮮ok wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個炒飯係特別在可以炒d公仔樣出黎<br />\n我淨係食天文台道個間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去食lunch<br />\n普通炒飯 佢用煙肉黎炒不特止 啲米比佢剁到勁撚碎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/173855_1b82bce50c8e98bb0d15e329628174e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F173855_1b82bce50c8e98bb0d15e329628174e4.jpg&h=96b654a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次都係比多少少食返海賀 山下"},{"pid":"e357175ae6e2ef4205980dddc538f3a879c243cb","tid":463093,"uid":39218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"五十嵐都冇，好打有限"},{"pid":"914a79efa94398065815d3951a56e12c54e4a812","tid":463093,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c3a16817e1081be03fcf4cf608f8da6a6cf349d","tid":463093,"uid":8511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"大戶屋啦"},{"pid":"235155d858dbdbc77999f8975e42d50979f00aee","tid":463093,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1d2d50c37753f0db5c04238d4017535785d6cda","tid":463093,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大戶屋啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大戶屋 +1<br />\n<br />\n不過尖咀嗰間執左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}